---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="小澤鶏卵｜新鮮で安心なたまごを地域へ"
  description="小澤鶏卵は地域の飲食店・施設・ご家庭へ、安全で高品質なたまごをお届けします。新鮮・安全・安定供給を大切にした卵の販売・卸売。"
>
  <Header />
  <main>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero" aria-label="ヒーローセクション">
      <div class="hero-bg">
        <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="hero-pattern"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="hero-label">Since 1965 — 地域とともに</p>
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          新鮮で安心なたまごを、<br />
          毎日の食卓へ
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
          小澤鶏卵は地域の飲食店・施設・ご家庭へ、<br class="hidden-mobile" />
          安全で高品質なたまごをお届けします。
        </p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">お問い合わせ</a>
          <a href="/products" class="btn-outline-light">商品案内</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-scroll" aria-hidden="true">
        <span>Scroll</span>
        <div class="scroll-line"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About -->
    <section class="about-section" id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-intro">
          <span class="section-label">About</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">小澤鶏卵について</h2>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <p class="about-text">
            地域の食卓を支えてきた小澤鶏卵。生産者との強い信頼関係のもと、
            毎日新鮮なたまごを安定的にお届けすることを第一に考えています。
            飲食店・福祉施設・学校給食から家庭用まで、幅広いニーズにお応えします。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="18" stroke="#4A7C59" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <path d="M20 10 C20 10 26 15 26 21 C26 24.3 23.3 27 20 27 C16.7 27 14 24.3 14 21 C14 15 20 10 20 10Z" fill="#4A7C59" opacity="0.3"/>
                <path d="M20 13 C20 13 24 17 24 21 C24 23.2 22.2 25 20 25 C17.8 25 16 23.2 16 21 C16 17 20 13 20 13Z" stroke="#4A7C59" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>地域密着</h3>
            <p>地域の皆様との長年の信頼関係を大切に、きめ細やかなサービスをご提供します。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <rect x="8" y="12" width="24" height="18" rx="2" stroke="#4A7C59" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <path d="M14 12V10C14 9.4 14.4 9 15 9H25C25.6 9 26 9.4 26 10V12" stroke="#4A7C59" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <path d="M8 18H32" stroke="#4A7C59" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.4"/>
                <path d="M15 23H25" stroke="#4A7C59" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>安定供給</h3>
            <p>業務用から家庭用まで、ご要望に合わせた安定的な納品体制を整えています。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M20 6 L32 12 V22 C32 28.6 26.6 34.4 20 36 C13.4 34.4 8 28.6 8 22 V12 L20 6Z" stroke="#4A7C59" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
                <path d="M14 21 L18 25 L26 17" stroke="#4A7C59" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>品質管理</h3>
            <p>徹底した鮮度・衛生管理により、安全で美味しいたまごをお届けします。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Products -->
    <section class="products-section">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="section-label">Products</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">商品案内</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p class="section-desc">用途やご要望に合わせた多彩な商品をご用意しています。</p>

        <div class="products-grid">
          <article class="product-card">
            <div class="product-img product-img--fresh" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="product-img-inner">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="egg-illustration">
                  <ellipse cx="100" cy="110" rx="55" ry="68" fill="#F5F0E8" stroke="#D4A017" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <ellipse cx="100" cy="108" rx="30" ry="36" fill="#F2C94C" opacity="0.4"/>
                  <ellipse cx="85" cy="90" rx="12" ry="8" fill="white" opacity="0.5" transform="rotate(-20, 85, 90)"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="product-info">
              <h3>新鮮たまご</h3>
              <p>毎朝入荷する新鮮なたまご。ご家庭での使い勝手を重視した個数でご用意しています。</p>
              <a href="/products#fresh" class="product-link">詳しく見る →</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="product-card">
            <div class="product-img product-img--business" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="product-img-inner">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="egg-illustration">
                  <ellipse cx="65" cy="115" rx="42" ry="52" fill="#F5F0E8" stroke="#D4A017" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <ellipse cx="135" cy="115" rx="42" ry="52" fill="#FAF7F2" stroke="#D4A017" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <ellipse cx="100" cy="100" rx="42" ry="55" fill="#F0EBE3" stroke="#D4A017" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <ellipse cx="100" cy="98" rx="22" ry="28" fill="#F2C94C" opacity="0.35"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="product-info">
              <h3>業務用たまご</h3>
              <p>飲食店・給食・製菓など、大量のご要望に対応。規格・サイズ別に安定供給いたします。</p>
              <a href="/products#business" class="product-link">詳しく見る →</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="product-card">
            <div class="product-img product-img--processed" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="product-img-inner">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="egg-illustration">
                  <circle cx="100" cy="115" r="55" fill="#F5F0E8" stroke="#D4A017" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <circle cx="100" cy="115" r="35" fill="#F2C94C" opacity="0.5"/>
                  <circle cx="100" cy="115" r="18" fill="#D4A017" opacity="0.6"/>
                  <ellipse cx="88" cy="103" rx="8" ry="5" fill="white" opacity="0.4" transform="rotate(-20, 88, 103)"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="product-info">
              <h3>温泉卵・加工品</h3>
              <p>こだわりの製法で仕上げた温泉卵や加工品。そのままお使いいただける便利な商品です。</p>
              <a href="/products#processed" class="product-link">詳しく見る →</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="products-cta">
          <a href="/products" class="btn-primary">すべての商品を見る</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Quality -->
    <section class="quality-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="quality-inner">
          <div class="quality-text">
            <span class="section-label">Quality</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">品質へのこだわり</h2>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <p>
              たまごの品質は、産地から食卓に届くまでの過程すべてにかかっています。
              小澤鶏卵では、鮮度・衛生・安全の三点を柱に、毎日の品質管理を徹底しています。
            </p>

            <ul class="quality-points">
              <li>
                <span class="quality-num">01</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>鮮度管理</strong>
                  <p>産地直送・当日入荷にこだわり、常に新鮮なたまごをお届けします。</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="quality-num">02</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>衛生管理</strong>
                  <p>保管・配送の全工程で温度・衛生基準を遵守しています。</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="quality-num">03</span>
                <div>
                  <strong>安全管理</strong>
                  <p>信頼できる生産者との連携で、安心・安全を確保しています。</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>

            <a href="/quality" class="btn-outline">品質への取り組みを見る</a>
          </div>

          <div class="quality-visual" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="quality-img-wrap">
              <div class="quality-pattern"></div>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 300 380" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="quality-egg-svg">
                <defs>
                  <linearGradient id="eggGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
                    <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#FAF7F2"/>
                    <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#F0EBE0"/>
                  </linearGradient>
                  <linearGradient id="yolkGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
                    <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#F2C94C"/>
                    <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#D4A017"/>
                  </linearGradient>
                </defs>
                <ellipse cx="150" cy="200" rx="100" ry="130" fill="url(#eggGrad)" stroke="#D4A017" stroke-width="1"/>
                <ellipse cx="150" cy="210" rx="55" ry="65" fill="url(#yolkGrad)" opacity="0.6"/>
                <ellipse cx="120" cy="170" rx="22" ry="14" fill="white" opacity="0.35" transform="rotate(-25, 120, 170)"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact CTA -->
    <section class="contact-cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="contact-cta-inner">
          <span class="section-label">Contact</span>
          <h2 class="cta-title">ご注文・お問い合わせ</h2>
          <p class="cta-text">
            業務用のご注文から個人のお客様まで、お気軽にご相談ください。<br />
            担当者が丁寧に対応いたします。
          </p>

          <div class="cta-contact-methods">
            <div class="cta-method">
              <div class="cta-method-icon">
                <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M6 7h5l2 5-2.5 1.5c1 2 2.5 3.5 4.5 4.5L16.5 15l5 2v5c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2C9.4 24 4 18.6 4 9c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z" stroke="#3D2B1F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="cta-method-label">お電話</p>
                <a href="tel:0000-00-0000" class="cta-phone">0000-00-0000</a>
                <p class="cta-method-note">月〜土 8:00〜17:00</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-method">
              <div class="cta-method-icon">
                <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <rect x="4" y="8" width="20" height="14" rx="2" stroke="#3D2B1F" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <path d="M4 10l10 7 10-7" stroke="#3D2B1F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="cta-method-label">メール</p>
                <a href="mailto:info@kozawa-keiran.com" class="cta-email">info@kozawa-keiran.com</a>
                <p class="cta-method-note">24時間受付・翌営業日ご返信</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-method">
              <div class="cta-method-icon">
                <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <rect x="4" y="6" width="20" height="16" rx="2" stroke="#3D2B1F" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <path d="M8 12h12M8 16h8" stroke="#3D2B1F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="cta-method-label">お問い合わせフォーム</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="cta-form-link">フォームはこちら</a>
                <p class="cta-method-note">詳細のご要望もお気軽に</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.97) 45%, rgba(242, 201, 76, 0.08) 100%);
  }

  .hero-pattern {
    position: absolute;
    right: -5%;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 55vw;
    max-width: 700px;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 50% 40% 50% 40%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 40% 40%, rgba(242, 201, 76, 0.12) 0%, rgba(212, 160, 23, 0.06) 50%, transparent 70%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 160, 23, 0.1);
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    padding-top: 72px;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--color-natural-green);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-dark-brown);
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.5vw, 1.05rem);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .hero-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-outline-light {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(61, 43, 31, 0.35);
    color: var(--color-dark-brown);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-outline-light:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-dark-brown);
    background-color: rgba(61, 43, 31, 0.05);
  }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2.5rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-scroll span {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(61, 43, 31, 0.3), transparent);
    animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes scrollPulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scaleY(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.8; transform: scaleY(1.2); transform-origin: top; }
  }

  /* About */
  .about-section {
    padding: 7rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-ivory);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .about-intro {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .about-text {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: var(--color-cream);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--color-egg-yellow);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-dark-brown);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Products */
  .products-section {
    padding: 7rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .section-desc {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .products-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .product-card {
    background-color: var(--color-ivory);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .product-img {
    height: 220px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .product-img--fresh { background-color: #F5F0E8; }
  .product-img--business { background-color: #EDE8DF; }
  .product-img--processed { background-color: #F0EBE3; }

  .product-img-inner {
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .egg-illustration {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .product-info {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .product-info h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-dark-brown);
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .product-info p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .product-link {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-natural-green);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: gap 0.2s;
  }

  .product-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .products-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  /* Quality */
  .quality-section {
    padding: 7rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-ivory);
  }

  .quality-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .quality-text p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .quality-points {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .quality-points li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .quality-num {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-egg-yellow);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .quality-points strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-dark-brown);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .quality-points p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .quality-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .quality-img-wrap {
    position: relative;
    width: 300px;
    height: 380px;
  }

  .quality-pattern {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 160, 23, 0.15);
    border-radius: 40% 60% 40% 60%;
  }

  .quality-egg-svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 24px rgba(61, 43, 31, 0.08));
  }

  /* Contact CTA */
  .contact-cta-section {
    padding: 7rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-green-light);
  }

  .contact-cta-inner {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    color: var(--color-dark-brown);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-text {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .cta-contact-methods {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

